test_odd_range:
assert [10, 8, 6, 4, 2, 0] == [121, 121]
  At index 0 diff: 10 != 121
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [121, 121]
  + [10, 8, 6, 4, 2, 0]
test_all_one_range:
assert [5, 3, 1] == [1, 1]
  At index 0 diff: 5 != 1
  Left contains one more item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1]
  + [5, 3, 1]
test_all_negative_ones:
assert [5, 3, 1] == [-1, -1]
  At index 0 diff: 5 != -1
  Left contains one more item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [-1, -1]
  + [5, 3, 1]
